### Story Writer — StoryWriterAgent
### POST /api/story/write
### Demonstrates: canRerun, @LlmTool, PersonaSpec, LlmOptions.withTemperature(),
###               ActionException.Permanent / .Transient, Bean Validation (JSR-380)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Short adventure story — full pipeline: validate → draft → review → revise → finalize
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/story/write
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storyId": "STORY-001",
  "theme": "A seasoned sea captain discovers a hidden island that appears only during a solar eclipse.",
  "genre": "Adventure",
  "targetAudience": "Young adults aged 16–25",
  "minWords": 200,
  "maxWords": 500
}

###

### Science fiction story — LLM gets higher temperature on draftStory
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/story/write
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storyId": "STORY-002",
  "theme": "In a distant future, humanity's last AI chooses to erase itself to protect free will.",
  "genre": "Science Fiction",
  "targetAudience": "Adults 25–45",
  "minWords": 400,
  "maxWords": 800
}

###

### Mystery story — shorter form
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/story/write
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storyId": "STORY-003",
  "theme": "A librarian finds a handwritten note inside a book returned 40 years overdue.",
  "genre": "Mystery",
  "targetAudience": "General audience",
  "minWords": 150,
  "maxWords": 350
}

###

### Validation failure — missing storyId → ActionException.Permanent
### Expected: 400 Bad Request or 5xx depending on platform error propagation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/story/write
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storyId": "",
  "theme": "A blank slate.",
  "genre": "Drama",
  "minWords": 100,
  "maxWords": 300
}

###

### Validation failure — maxWords too large → ActionException.Permanent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/story/write
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storyId": "STORY-BAD",
  "theme": "Over the limit.",
  "genre": "Drama",
  "minWords": 100,
  "maxWords": 9999
}
